        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This bill expands tax-exempt governmental pension plans to include plans maintained by a tax-exempt public safety agency all of whose employees are emergency response providers performing firefighting services or out-of-hospital emergency medical services.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
